## FILE 1: `src/app/pages/itemLibrary/thumbnail/item-thumbnail.component.ts`

AG-Grid cell renderer (`ICellRendererAngularComp`). Selector `app-item-thumbnail`.

Inject: `MatDialog` (from `@angular/material/dialog`), `HelperService` (from `src/app/helpers/services/helper.service`), `ConfigService` (from `src/app/helpers/services/config.service`).

Properties:
- `imgSrc: string | null = null`
- `itemNum = ''`
- `propertyHue = 220`
- `hasImage = false`

`agInit(params)` / `refresh(params)` logic:
- `itemNum = params.data?.itemNum || ''`
- Hash `String(params.data?.property || params.data?.property_id || '')` → `propertyHue`
- If `params.data?.pic?.Thumbnail` exists: `imgSrc = helperService.buildPublicUrl(params.data.pic.Thumbnail)`, `hasImage = true`
- Else if `params.data?.pic?.FullSizePicture`: use that
- Else: `imgSrc = null`, `hasImage = false`
- `refresh` returns `true`

`onImageClick()` method: opens `imageEditorComponent` (import from `../imageEditor/imageEditor.component`) via MatDialog with `data: { FullSizePicture: imgSrc, Thumbnail: imgSrc }`, `maxWidth: '95vw'`, `maxHeight: '95vh'`. Only call if `hasImage`.

Getters:
- `tileGradient`: `linear-gradient(150deg, hsl(${propertyHue} 46% 95%), hsl(${propertyHue} 40% 87%))`
- `tileBorderColor`: `hsl(${propertyHue} 30% 80%)`
- `glyphColor`: `hsl(${propertyHue} 42% 34%)`

